metadata.description: Once upon a time, there was an artist named Yoshi Mari. All she wanted was to let people see, through her art, nature as she does. From branding artisan’s companies to drawing children’s books, one thing was clear to her eyes: her connection to planet earth. When the time has arrived, and all the right stars have lined up together, Yoshi felt this was the right moment to use her power of expression to take direct action…
metadata.name: #1 | The Search
